---
// src/components/CatalogCTA.astro
---
<section class="py-20 bg-gray-900 overflow-hidden relative">
  <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-[#B8E900]/10 rounded-full blur-3xl pointer-events-none -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
  
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-black to-gray-800 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl border border-white/10 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
      
      <div class="flex-1 text-center md:text-left">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-[#B8E900]/20 text-[#B8E900] text-xs font-bold mb-6 border border-[#B8E900]/30">
          <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-[#B8E900] animate-pulse"></span>
          PDF ATUALIZADO 2025
        </div>
        
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4 leading-tight">
          Tenha o portfólio completo <br/>
          <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-[#B8E900] to-green-500">na palma da sua mão.</span>
        </h2>
        
        <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed max-w-xl mx-auto md:mx-0">
          Acesse offline todas as especificações técnicas, tabelas de medidas e linhas exclusivas da Nicopel. Ideal para compartilhar com sua equipe.
        </p>
        
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center md:justify-start">
          <a 
            href="https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/14lWE-CXd9rEUD4La-mUStDq8HZqwCU5G?usp=sharing" 
            target="_blank"
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-[#B8E900] text-black font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-[#B8E900]/30 group transform hover:-translate-y-1"
          >
            <svg class="w-5 h-5 mr-2 group-hover:animate-bounce" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 16v1a3 3 0 003 3h10a3 3 0 003-3v-1m-4-4l-4 4m0 0l-4-4m4 4V4"></path></svg>
            Baixar Catálogo PDF
          </a>

          <a href="https://api.whatsapp.com/message/KB4JJZXMVMWXP1" target="_blank" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-transparent border-2 border-white/20 text-white font-bold rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 transition-all">
            Solicitar no WhatsApp
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="relative w-full md:w-1/3 max-w-[280px] hidden md:block">
        <div class="relative z-10 bg-neutral-100 rounded-r-lg rounded-l-sm shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] transform -rotate-6 border-l-4 border-gray-300 aspect-[3/4] flex flex-col overflow-hidden group hover:rotate-0 transition-transform duration-500 cursor-pointer">
           <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[#111] p-6 flex flex-col justify-between">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 border-2 border-[#B8E900] rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
                  <span class="text-[#B8E900] font-bold text-xl">N</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                  <h3 class="text-3xl font-black text-white uppercase leading-none mb-1">Catálogo</h3>
                  <p class="text-[#B8E900] font-bold tracking-[0.2em] text-sm">PRODUTOS 2025</p>
              </div>
              <div class="h-1 w-20 bg-[#B8E900]"></div>
           </div>
           <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-transparent via-white/10 to-transparent pointer-events-none"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="absolute -bottom-8 left-4 right-4 h-4 bg-black/60 blur-lg rounded-full"></div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>